How to Get Better Generation Results

1. Set the Strength_model parameter of all three models to 1.

2. Upload landscape or square images instead of vertical ones.

3. Upload front-facing photos of people or objects rather than side views.

4. Set the "target_size" of the "#14 qweneditutils" node to 1536, and run the workflow using a 2XLarge machine.
